snippet.title: Lonely Mountains: Downhill - Leaked Trailer Footage
snippet.description:
ATTENTION!!!
There seems to be some leaked footage from our latest trailer shoot. We want to assure everyone that nobody has been seriously injured and that our rider is on the way to recovery.
